    description2: `The District Committee of VKL /o/ appointed me head of two sites, which includes 44 houses on Zagorodniy Ave, Izhdunarodniy etc. I had to split into brigades and deploy the work. The slogan: "Everyone to fight for the cleanliness of the city".`,
