    description2: `We are digging the ground around our barracks. The ground is hard, it must have been trampled on for a hundred years, and nothing has ever grown on it. But we dig, we dig everything. In the city center they dig up all the newspapers, squares - everything, everything for vegetables! Mine on Serdobolskaya also got a plot in the yard of the house. I helped dig and saw a lot of brick crumbs in the ground. Will vegetables grow? Sasheta is digging up some fertilizer (feces). She is completely dried up, but she is not discouraged, she is working.`,
