    description2: `Meeting of workers. The report was made by the secretary of the District Committee t. Neid. The meeting was attended by the Hero of the Soviet Union tanker Comrade Yakovleva and the Order Bearer Comrade Kupriyanov. Comrade Yakovlev in his speech simply and figuratively told how our Red Army, and in particular he, crushed the fascist murderers. One after another episodes of the fight against the fascist scum are passing through the red thread. "War on cunning - who outsmarts whom, says Comrade Yakovlev, and I decided to outsmart the Germans: when my tank at the very front edge was hit, damaged, I took off my overcoat, stuffed an effigy and put. The tents would be spread out and the Germans would beat on this effigy and tents, while I fixed the tank with my comrades in the meantime; within one and a half to two hours the tank was repaired and I went forward. Then I destroyed two hundred Germans." The meeting was held with a great uplift.`,
